headline: Glenn Martens, fashion at high-voltage
description: 'Essence of a Style' (4/6). Appointed to the helm of some of the biggest fashion houses, six designers are set to command the industry's attention this season. In this chapter, the former artistic director of the label Y/Project, now at Maison Margiela while continuing his work for Diesel.

headline: The meteoric rise and exploited fame of Jean Pormanove, French streamer who died on-air
